quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  16,75,DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN ‘ABDÆN MEMLUKÆN LA JEKDIRU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE MEN REZEKNAHU MINNA RIZKÆN HESENÆN FEHUWE JUNFIKU MINHU SIRRÆN WE XHEHRÆN HEL JESTEWUNEL-HEMDU LILLAHI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,76,WE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN REXHULEJNI ‘EHEDUHUMA ‘EBKEMU LA JEKDIRU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE HUWE KELLUN ‘ALA MEWLAHU ‘EJNEMA JUWEXHXHHHHU LA JE’TI BIHAJRIN HEL JESTEWI HUWE WE MEN JE’MURU BIL-’ADLI WE HUWE ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  16,77,WE LILLEHI GAJBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA ‘EMRU ES-SA’ATI ‘ILLA KELEMHIL-BESERI ‘EW HUWE ‘EKREBU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  16,78,WEL-LAHU ‘EHREXHEKUM MIN BUTUNI ‘UMMEHATIKUM LA TA’LEMUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUMU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WEL-’EF’IDETE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  16,79,‘ELEM JEREW ‘ILAT-TEJRI MUSEHHARATIN FI XHEWWI ES-SEMA’I MA JUMSIKUHUNNE ‘ILLALLAHU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  16,80,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN BUJUTIKUM SEKENÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN XHULUDIL-’EN’AMI BUJUTÆN TESTEHIFFUNEHA JEWME DHA’NIKUM WE JEWME ‘IKAMETIKUM WE MIN ‘ESWAFIHA WE ‘EWBARIHA WE ‘ESH’ARIHA ‘ETHATHÆN WE META’ÆN ‘ILA HININ
  16,81,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIMMA HALEKA DHILALÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MINEL-XHIBALI ‘EKNANÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM SERABILE TEKIKUMUL-HERRE WE SERABILE TEKIKUM BE’SEKUM KEDHALIKE JUTIMMU NI’METEHU ‘ALEJKUM LE’ALLEKUM TUSLIMUNE
  16,82,FE’IN TEWELLEW FE’INNEMA ‘ALEJKEL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  16,83,JA’RIFUNE NI’METEL-LAHI THUMME JUNKIRUNEHA WE ‘EKTHERUHUMUL-KAFIRUNE
  16,84,WE JEWME NEB’ATHU MIN KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN THUMME LA JU’UDHENU LILLEDHINE KEFERU WE LA HUM JUSTA’TEBUNE
  16,85,WE ‘IDHA RE’AL-LEDHINE DHELEMUL-’ADHABE FELA JUHAFFEFU ‘ANHUM WE LA HUM JUNDHERUNE
  16,86,WE ‘IDHA RE’AL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU SHUREKA’EHUM KALU REBBENA HA’UULA’ SHUREKA’UUNAL-LEDHINE KUNNA NED’U MIN DUNIKE FE’ELKAW ‘ILEJHIMUL-KAWLE ‘INNEKUM LEKADHIBUNE
  16,87,WE ‘ELKAW ‘ILA ELLAHI JEWME’IDHIN ES-SELEME WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  16,88,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI ZIDNAHUM ‘ADHABÆN FEWKAL-’ADHABI BIMA KANU JUFSIDUNE
  16,89,WE JEWME NEB’ATHU FI KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN ‘ALEJHIM MIN ‘ENFUSIHIM WE XHI’NA BIKE SHEHIDÆN ‘ALA HA’UULA’ WE NEZZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE TIBJANÆN LIKULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN WE BUSHRA LILMUSLIMINE